      <div class="modal">
        <div class="instruct">
        <p>Welcome to Superdisco!</p>
        <p>Here anyone can be an amazing DJ if you follow these rules:</p>
        <p>Click on the squares to create some epic tunes. Make sure to choose
        2 of the purple squares, 2 of the pink suares and any combination of 4
        of the blue squares. When you hit 8...Superdisco! You can remove and add
        squares to create your own hits</p>
        </div>
        <div id="play">
  <p id='play'><a href='#'>
    PLAY
  </a></p>
</div>
      </div>
    </div>
